Late again?

670
00:37:35,945 --> 00:37:36,505
Sorry.

671
00:37:36,744 --> 00:37:37,664
I'm late.

672
00:37:38,584 --> 00:37:39,104
Well?

673
00:37:39,104 --> 00:37:40,264
