678
00:37:47,825 --> 00:37:48,488
Hello, Mr. Lin.

679
00:37:48,488 --> 00:37:49,264
Hello, Mr. Barry.

680
00:37:49,264 --> 00:37:51,144
I'd like to thank you on behalf of GST.

681
00:37:51,144 --> 00:37:52,144
You're too kind.

682
00:37:52,544 --> 00:37:55,144
Next time you're in Nanjiang,
