683
00:37:55,425 --> 00:37:56,224
Alright.

684
00:37:56,224 --> 00:37:56,945
Please carry on.

685
00:37:56,945 --> 00:37:57,825
I'll toast you later.

686
00:38:00,865 --> 00:38:01,465
Long time.

687
00:38:03,385 --> 00:38:06,264
These distributors are eager
to break into Guangzhou,

688
