691
00:38:14,385 --> 00:38:15,345
So, Mr. Shen...

692
00:38:15,664 --> 00:38:17,345
They have no ties to Mr. Shen.

693
00:38:19,704 --> 00:38:20,385
So you...

694
00:38:20,385 --> 00:38:21,425
I'm with GST.

695
00:38:21,425 --> 00:38:22,385
No matter what,

696
00:38:22,865 --> 00:38:25,385
