Sorry I didn't come down to greet you.

701
00:38:35,305 --> 00:38:36,664
Long time no see.

702
00:38:37,104 --> 00:38:37,865
Long time no see.

703
00:38:37,865 --> 00:38:38,825
Long time no see.

704
00:38:39,025 --> 00:38:39,624
Come on.

705
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:41,224
This is Barry.

706
