Have a seat.

709
00:38:48,905 --> 00:38:50,184
Please sit.

710
00:38:53,624 --> 00:38:54,945
Nice to meet you, Barry.

711
00:38:54,945 --> 00:38:55,624
Nice to meet you.

712
00:38:55,744 --> 00:38:56,584
